text: Arthur Spaenhoven (born 9 April 1934) is a Belgian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 57 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Belgium Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp Category:People from Hoboken
